<template>
  <CalendarComp :attributes='attrs' />
  <!-- <DatePicker /> -->
</template>



<script>
// import { Calendar, DatePicker } from 'v-calendar';
// import Calendar from 'v-calendar';

export default {
  data() {
    return {
      attrs: [
        {
          key: 'today',
          highlight: true,
          dates: new Date(),
        },
      ],
    };
  },
};
</script>
